{"tid":2075549,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港國際商會：海外人才不願來港 「國安法損法治保護傘」","createTime":"2020-06-23T02:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T03:03:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb71a40941a90880b72b3464c6d5a270f74a7dc6","tid":2075549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:22:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/FWTBS5NP23MOAGMDOFY3RDBFE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FFWTBS5NP23MOAGMDOFY3RDBFE4%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7rAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=ed07b424\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FFWTBS5NP23MOAGMDOFY3RDBFE4%2F&h=efa4d1ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/FWTBS5NP23MOAGMDOFY3RDBFE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港國際商會：海外人才不願來港<br />\n「國安法損法治保護傘」<br />\n<br />\n【惡法臨城】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自北京堅持在港落實港版國安法後，北京及港府雖然一再表示無損香港國際金融中心地位及外商利益，但始終無法穩定投資者信心。國際商會─香港區會（The International Chamber of Commerce - Hong Kong）昨發表港版國安法意見書，直指北京做法令人震驚，批評立法情況不清晰，令外國投資者恐懼和失去信心，「令人極之擔憂是將來進一步破壞這個保護傘的先例」。有金融界人士更指，港版國安法較逃犯條例更令投資者不安，他們對香港法治失去信心，不少海外投資者已有兩手準備，準備隨時撤出香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-IED7piJnYlm14Hy20DPTpDvNWw=/802x531/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LBF6KFNVRB6W5H3WOU2CCOKAR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-IED7piJnYlm14Hy20DPTpDvNWw%3D%2F802x531%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLBF6KFNVRB6W5H3WOU2CCOKAR4.jpg&h=6c18373c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京堅持在港落實港版國安法，國際商會─香港區會批評令外國投資者恐懼和失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n北京及港府一直宣稱，落實港版國安法對外商及香港投資環境有利，但外資想法似並非如此。國際商會─香港區會昨發表意見書，指中央政府最近突提出代香港制訂國家安全法令人震驚，認為中央政府事前並未徵詢香港市民意見，做法「令人惋惜，也摧毀港人對中央政府的信心」；又批評目前立法情況既不清晰，又有很多不確定因素，令人對香港經濟及個人自由和安全感到憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：安倍利誘港金融機構落戶東京<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對另設法庭處理國安案件<br />\n<br />\n國際商會要求在人大常委會通過港版國安法前，中港兩地政府應予。。。。。損害有關屏障，「更令人極之擔憂是將來進一步破壞這個保護傘的先例。」<br />\n<br />\n商會又對港版國安法提。。。。。單位，更表明反對香港另設法庭處理國安法的案件。<br />\n<br />\n除了國際商會，早前兩度調。。。。。，亦足夠維持中港兩地間、現時評級相差一級的距離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惠譽：倘實施或再影響評級<br />\n<br />\n資深對沖基金經理、「2047香港監察」召集人錢志健表示，。。。。。，有兩手準備，兩制冇咗，佢咪會轉移業務去其他普通法地區。」<br />\n<br />\n錢續指，他2000年回流香港，。。。。。，咁對投資者資產保障會減少。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2K4LCBMEVOEGZINOBNCMVMPDMI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2K4LCBMEVOEGZINOBNCMVMPDMI.gif&h=86b085ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30ff21def1f79f5b2b5e2af355d65bbfd3ca67f4","tid":2075549,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"後知後覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3810d3fb875f188f4c1db5ef5b48991ce65f7dc5","tid":2075549,"uid":188362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"國內無人才咩？ <br />\n咪請國內人材黎囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好取代哂啲藍絲 <br />\n咁撚愛國 讓埋份工比人啦"},{"pid":"190bc23f9a6f512298d35d193ff4d5094ebeb94b","tid":2075549,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LhfB3Tu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhfB3Tu.gif&h=0251850c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55bafbace00c0d91a0a92306852e431c5f757c87","tid":2075549,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3810d3fb875f188f4c1db5ef5b48991ce65f7dc5","tid":2075549,"uid":188362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"國內無人才咩？ <br />\n咪請國內人材黎囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好取代哂啲藍絲 <br />\n咁撚愛國 讓埋份工比人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0